Title: Andrews heat exchanger
Description: This Andrews brand heat exchanger is designed for use in CWH and LCWH appliances. The heat exchanger transfers heat from a boiler's burner to water. A primary heat exchanger is found in all boilers, using heat from a burner to raise the temperature of the water in the system while a secondary heat exchanger is present only in combis and allows the heat to be transferred between closed systems.

Title: Andrews hot surface igniter
Description: A genuine Andrews spare, this hot surface igniter is designed for use in the brand's CWH and LCWH units. The most commonly used electronic ignition system, a hot surface ignitor works by heating up when electricity passes through it. Ordinarily made of silicon nitride and silicon carbide ceramic, the igniter’s heat ignites the gas on the opening of the gas valve.
category: Parts and Spares/sub_categories/Heating Replacement Parts/sub_categories/Water Heater Parts and Accessories/Water Heater Parts and Accessories.csv -> Andrews hot surface igniter

Title: Andrews fan
Description: A genuine Andrews part, this fan is suitable for CWH and LCWH range boilers. The fan introduces fresh air into a boiler's combustion chamber, ensuring that gas is burnt correctly and extracting burnt gas at the end of the combustion process. Your boiler's safety parameters ensure that no gas passes through to the main burner if the fan is not functioning correctly.
